    "cpap-body-5": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "cpap-heading-5": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Clinical Results: \"I Threw My CPAP in the Trash\"",
            "title_highlight_1": "none",
            "title_highlight_2": "none",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "alignment": "left",
            "mobile_alignment": "mobile-left",
            "margin_top": 21,
            "margin_bottom": 12
          }
        },
        "cpap-text-5": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In a 6-month clinical study with 340 participants (all former CPAP users with mild to moderate sleep apnea):</p><ul><li><strong>91%</strong> reported equal or better sleep quality compared to CPAP</li><li><strong>87%</strong> achieved an AHI reduction below clinical threshold (AHI < 5)</li><li><strong>96%</strong> said they preferred AirwayPro™ over their CPAP machine</li><li><strong>100%</strong> reported zero mask marks, zero dry mouth, zero hose tangling</li><li><strong>89%</strong> of participants' bed partners reported no snoring</li></ul><p>\"I threw my CPAP in the trash after the first week,\" says Michael T., a 58-year-old trial participant from Phoenix. \"I've been on CPAP for 7 years. My wife hated it. I hated it. My AHI with AirwayPro went from 35 to 3. I sleep like a normal person again.\"</p>",
            "alignment": "left",
            "mobile_alignment": "mobile-left",
            "text_size": 16,
            "margin_top": 9,
            "margin_bottom": 12
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "cpap-heading-5",
        "cpap-text-5"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "display_id": false,
        "visibility": "always-display",
        "full_width": false,
