    },
    "cpap-body-8": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "cpap-heading-8": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Try AirwayPro™ Risk-Free for 90 Nights",
            "title_highlight_1": "none",
            "title_highlight_2": "none",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "alignment": "left",
            "mobile_alignment": "mobile-left",
            "margin_top": 21,
            "margin_bottom": 12
          }
        },
        "cpap-text-8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Dr. Crawford is so confident AirwayPro™ will change your sleep that he's offering a <strong>90-night risk-free trial</strong>. Use it every night for three full months. If you don't sleep better than you ever did with CPAP, return it for a full refund — no questions asked.</p><p>AirwayPro™ is currently available at an introductory price — <strong>40% off</strong> the planned retail price — but only while initial inventory lasts. Given that 22 million Americans have sleep apnea and the first production run was 50,000 units, availability won't last long.</p>",
            "alignment": "left",
            "mobile_alignment": "mobile-left",
            "text_size": 16,
            "margin_top": 9,
            "margin_bottom": 21
          }
        },
